  "title": "Brand Ambassador",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Fresh graduate, recently ORD-ed, or considering a career transition?</strong><br>\nThis opportunity offers a strong foundation for individuals looking to develop professionally in a dynamic and growth-oriented environment.</h3>\n<p><strong>No prior experience is required.</strong><br>\nComprehensive training and guidance will be provided to ensure you acquire the necessary skills and confidence to excel in the role.</p>\n<h2><strong>Key Responsibilities &amp; Exposure</strong></h2>\n<h3><strong>Events and Roadshows</strong></h3>\n<p>Participate in organised events and roadshows, where you will engage with the public and represent various brands in a professional manner.</p>\n<h3><strong>B2B Campaigns</strong></h3>\n<p>Be involved in business-to-business marketing campaigns, gaining real-world exposure and strengthening your communication and presentation abilities.</p>\n<h3><strong>Client Interaction</strong></h3>\n<p>Conduct direct, face-to-face engagements with clients. This will enhance your interpersonal skills and allow you to develop strong customer relations.</p>\n<h3><strong>Professional Team Environment</strong></h3>\n<p>Work within a supportive and performance-driven team that encourages learning, growth, and continuous improvement.</p>\n<h3><strong>Development Workshops</strong></h3>\n<p>Attend regular training workshops focused on communication, leadership, sales techniques, and personal development.</p>\n<h2><strong>Benefits &amp; Opportunities</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Open to <strong>18+ Singaporeans/PRs</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Weekly earnings</strong> with <strong>uncapped commissions</strong></li>\n  <li>Attractive <strong>performance incentives</strong></li>\n  <li>Ongoing <strong>upskilling workshops</strong></li>\n  <li>Clear <strong>leadership advancement pathways</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Travel opportunities</strong> for further exposure and training</li>\n  <li>A positive and encouraging work culture that values progress</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><strong>Take the Next Step in Your Career</strong></h1>\n<p>If you are motivated, eager to learn, and looking for a role that offers both personal development and career progression, we encourage you to apply.</p>\n<p><strong>Positions are limited.<br>\nPlease contact us to submit your application before slots are filled.</strong></p>",
